    eligibility: `NC resident; have HIV; have a gross family income at or below 300% FPL; not have any third party-coverage; and have at least one prescription for any medication on the ADAP formulary. Clients on SPAP pay their Medicare Part D premiums and SPAP pays their out of pocket costs for all medications on the ADAP formulary. All ADAP clients who are eligible for Medicare Part D must enroll in a Medicare Part D plan and pay the plan premiums.`,
